QuestData.Title: Flamefly Trap
QuestData.Description: Ol' Winky still hasn't come back! Now I'm gettin' worried.$B$BDo me a favor and get another one of those flameflies from Upper Blackrock Spire. If we get enough of em,' Winky's sure to see the glimmer and come heading on back.$B$BAn then we'll have him right where we want him!
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect a Spire Flamefly in Upper Blackrock Spire.
